Meru Governor Kiraitu Murungi, His Tharaka Nithi Counterpart Muthomi Njuki, And Industry CS Peter Munya Have Lauded Meru Council Of Elders, Njuri Ncheke For Uniting Meru And Tharaka Nithi Counties To Push The Development Agenda. They Lauded Njuri Ncheke Elders For Setting Their Differences Aside Paving The Way For Peace And Stability In The Region. The Leaders Spoke At Chiru Shrine During A Unity Meeting That Saw The Installation Of New Council Leaders.